{"tid":1550672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你係要做和事佬 唔想手足因為衝動而打死人既","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T17:36:02.000Z","uid":201644,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"94bde796041ac35ea218691e96d7c505dcdac805","tid":1550672,"uid":201644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:03:55.000Z","msg":"好心你就唔好阻住啲手足啦 係側邊叫唔好打死人咪得囉 而家手足俾人拉啦 你自己就滿足完你所謂既同理心 就走咗去 你都好過份"},{"pid":"b5a89f145cc7dab3584af78ed6258526c2fe8045","tid":1550672,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:04:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1676eebe2c13ddcc514da1d9e5d25e9f146a6ea4","tid":1550672,"uid":201644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:07:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53b927de8d24e8a167e90c2b49edd0f13e330a64","tid":1550672,"uid":201644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c29ec426d456ab295e65bb07498eec7cb10a8c","tid":1550672,"uid":201644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:14:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d35df31a9b203e7528cbca83101ca9d1ef24846","tid":1550672,"uid":201644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:14:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40a5afb36c36d23e2315035fc03d4be16db9d312","tid":1550672,"uid":201644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:14:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f0dbb22ac3e3a5876090cbd740295d192f74a53","tid":1550672,"uid":204750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:15:19.000Z","msg":"左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e180d4fa9c114d276d99e5311f7b14ebe4d843ad","tid":1550672,"uid":201644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:15:41.000Z","msg":"唔好打死人"},{"pid":"bec9ac07886422af9ee8aae12943f545dd69b97f","tid":1550672,"uid":201644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:15:53.000Z","msg":"唔好打死人"},{"pid":"091c07449b295753fb18478c89b561462fff7021","tid":1550672,"uid":201644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:16:25.000Z","msg":"唔好打死人"},{"pid":"1c64fe07593aa65438d1e29877e2917bb97367a9","tid":1550672,"uid":201644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:17:28.000Z","msg":"唔好打死人"},{"pid":"d47567e706bd1aaa7fc0db12f91cf743020474b7","tid":1550672,"uid":182061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:17:30.000Z","msg":"下次在場唔該有人大叫開遮，叫埋左膠開遮"},{"pid":"536055d625ba5e3cf4f710499ef5c8291ed0230b","tid":1550672,"uid":1315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:18:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阻撚住哂死阻膠 屌你老母 出刀唔見你第一時間出黎擋</span>"},{"pid":"f8f4c65b14405b4751e7932ecc2226e7b54f97c2","tid":1550672,"uid":254558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:18:58.000Z","msg":"【修訂版】元朗9.9七點三有人鏈<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dQmteS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dQmteS</a>"},{"pid":"d21bba78d39fa354cf52e5437ab6bee1059aebdb","tid":1550672,"uid":204750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:21:39.000Z","msg":"屌晒你班左膠撚"},{"pid":"da35fcf36c1ac909e1a7ae0f102f880c525e5f06","tid":1550672,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:25:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">左膠永遠都唔係同路人<br />\n<br />\n荃灣黑夜 要前線放藍衫走<br />\n結果同一班藍衫轉頭斬斷其他手足手筋腳筋攪到個手足殘廢 同有手足比人爆頭<br />\n到今日岩岩機場 逼手足放個用磚頭爆手足頭既藍絲走<br />\n<br />\n重有依2個月好多單左膠死攬傷人者<br />\n根本班撚樣只係為光環 欺善怕惡<br />\n對住黑社會就淆底唔敢阻黑社會斬人<br />\n對住自己手足 知手足唔會打佢地<br />\n就大大力阻手足還拖 同講廢話訓前線話<br />\n話會扣幾多分 會失民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"b1bcb7944d708bfad8118c562a4e9530dec5b146","tid":1550672,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:27:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不要說 「 左膠 」<br />\n<br />\n試着說 「 藍絲臥底 」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阻人嗰啲藍絲扮架，支持送中，支持警察架"},{"pid":"cb547a8a0ececf4d7c6591b63848838a7415e383","tid":1550672,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:33:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5d220953f0462ad7c3d5f1a5fc1da04fb55ede","tid":1550672,"uid":201644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:36:02.000Z","msg":"唔好打死人"}]}